header.advice__title
  | <em>{{spaceContext.space.data.name}}</em> has no content types yet
button.cfnext-btn-action--large-popout-icon.ct-empty-list__action(type="button"
    ng-click="entityCreationController.newContentType()"
    ng-hide="permissionController.shouldHide('createContentType')"
    ng-disabled="permissionController.shouldDisable('createContentType')"
    cf-when-disabled="createContentType")
  cf-icon(name="new-ct")
  | Create content type

